    feat(scene): add scene primitive library expansion
    
    Add 6 new scene primitives for library_room and ruins_courtyard templates:
    - tileset: floor_stone_01, wall_library_01, cobble_01
    - prop_sheet: bookshelf_01, ruins_pillar_01, rubble_01
    
